Class Journal

java.lang.Object
  data.Journal
All Implemented Interfaces:
java.io.Serializable
public class Journal
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.io.Serializable

The Journal class contains all of the information of a user. It has a list of every type of entry available and it also stores the preferences made by the user.

Author:
Everyone
